nodes.text: Danny Keller is a storyboard and previsualization artist, and an episode director (starting in Season 4) for Star Wars: The Clone Wars, a CGI-based television series that debuted October 3, 2008 on Cartoon Network as a continuation of the film with the same name, released two months prior. Keller is also serving as head of animation for the mobile game Star Wars: Uprising.
